et_pb_text][et_pb_text admin_label=\"Text\" background_layout=\"light\" text_orientation=\"left\" use_border_color=\"off\" border_color=\"#ffffff\" border_style=\"solid\"]\r\n\r\nMaui Beats provides professional DJ/MC/Sound &amp; Lighting services for your Company Events! Â Â From promotional events to holiday parties, Maui Beats can help you curate and coordinate an amazing night of music &amp; fun!\r\n\r\nWe have performed at most major venues all over Maui including Ritz-Carlton, Hyatt, &amp; more!\r\n\r\nFormer clients such as Beats Audio, Intel, HP, Golden Gates National Parks Conservancy, Maui Ag Fest, Hawaii Yoga Festival, Maui Yoga Festival &amp; 2014 Maroon 5 after-party @ The Grand Wailea.\r\nMaui Beats has years of experience playing at diverse events &amp; a mastery in handling all types of gatherings. Â This experience has led our DJâ€™s to hone an extremely individualized approach to working with clients, so clients can be assured the music for their event can be custom tailored to their expectations.\r\n\r\n[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][et_pb_column type=\"1_3\"][et_pb_text admin_label=\"Text\" background_layout=\"light\" text_orientation=\"left\" use_border_color=\"off\" border_color=\"#ffffff\" border_style=\"solid\"]\r\n\r\nOur DJs at Maui Beats have always been thorough and professional in every aspect of their business. Â From making themselves accessible to the client for every aspect of event planning (by email, phone, or in person), to using the highest quality equipment, they make sure that the client always feels confident that their event will be a success.\r\n\r\nWe specialize in DJ\'s but can offer ALL entertainment for your event!\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Live Music</li>\r\n 	<li>Bands</li>\r\n 	<li>DJâ€™s</li>\r\n 	<li>Hula</li>\r\n 	<li>Fire dancers</li>\r\n 	<li>Performers</li>\r\n 	<li>Theme Parties</li>\r\n 	<li>Uplighting, Fog Machines &amp; other party toys!</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[/et_pb_text][/et_pb_column][/et_pb_row][/et_pb_section][et_pb_se